  <div class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2">First Prototype Design Concept</div>

  <div class="w-full" style="margin-top: 20px; text-align: justify;">
    <p>
      For the first prototype, we designed a drive test setup to assess the functionality of our self-developed 
      cycloidal drives, motors, and initial control algorithms. We have also created a preliminary prototype of the exoskeleton using additive manufacturing 
      methods to ensure the proper assembly of all parts. We aimed to refine this prototype by improving the actuation system by using a linear actuator, metallizing 
      the prototype, and build a full Digital Twin of the exoskeleton. Below is a concept video of our first prototype.
